      <p>Generic 30-day reorder for Great Dane kibble and cat treats alike. Life-stage transition invisible until churn. New pet onboarding skipped for forum traffic signups. Multi-pet households on single consumption timer.</p>
      <p>Reading path for pet products: pet profile fields at signup; Sequenzy {segment.emailPriorities.join('; ')}; {segment.metrics[0]} by segment weekly. {segment.buyingCycle} and life-stage transitions govern Shopify email marketing apps triggers — not generic DTC timers.</p>
